            <li><strong>Second year:</strong> +9 human years (24 total)</li>
            <li><strong>Each year after:</strong> +4-7 years (depending on size)</li>
          </ul>
        </div>

        <h2>Size Matters: Breed-Specific Aging</h2>

        <p>One of the most significant discoveries in canine aging research is the impact of breed size on lifespan and aging patterns:</p>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 my-8">
          <div class="bg-green-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-green-900 mb-3">Small Dogs (Under 25 lbs)</h3>
